* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.10 (2022-11-05)

When an archive file is executable, show the archive file colour
Implemented vertical panel layout, invokable via command line option '-v', or via ALT-V key combination

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.9 (2022-08-05)

The glob pattern when (un)tagging files is now case insensitive

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.8 (2022-01-06)

Minor cosmetic fix when tagging files
Fix crash when going from an empty directory to a non-existent bookmark
Fix crash when launching rnr from a deleted directory
Fix crash when creating multiple directories

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.7 (2021-08-16)

Don't report error if the file system does not support copystat
Don't do synchronous filesystem operations if they are not logged to the database. This is a tremendous speedup.

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.6 (2021-05-31)

Catch OSError instead of (FileNotFoundError, PermissionError). This should fix some crashes.

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.5 (2021-05-03)

If archivefs (https://github.com/bugnano/archivefs) is installed, use it instead of archivemount

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.4 (2021-03-28)

Fix crash with filenames containing Unicode surrogates

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.3 (2021-03-04)

The man pages are installed in the share/man/ directory instead of just man/
Fix crash with filenames containing East Asian Unicode characters

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.2 (2020-12-02)

Added command 'x' to execute file
Updated the bash and fish wrappers to return the exit code
Fix hangup on error message
Fix macros referring to archive files

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.1 (2020-11-26)

Changed classifier to Production/Stable

* Noteworthy changes in release 1.0.0 (2020-11-26)

First stable release

